# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者賭博入面，因為輸錢太多，決定唔再落注或者賣出股票，盡量減少損失。通常指喺蝕錢嘅情況下，停止繼續投資，避免損失擴大。
eng:to cut losses (in investment or gambling)
<eg>
yue:佢見個股跌到咁犀利，唯有止蝕，唔可以等住套返。 (keoi5 gin3 go3 gu2 dit3 dou3 gam2 sai1 lei6, wai4 jau5 ji2 sik1, m4 ho2 ji5 dang2 zyu6 tou3 faan1.)
eng:Seeing the stock price falling so sharply, he had no choice but to cut his losses and couldn't wait for it to recover.
 [end of text]


